Influencing `ADOC''s pedanticness
=================================

`--no-warnings'
     `ADOC' will not print *any* warnings.

`--check-keywords'
     `ADOC' will complain about section title keywords which are not in
     the example below.

`--check-presence'
     `ADOC' will complain if one of the keywords in the example below
     is missing in a function description.

`--pedantic'
     `ADOC' will complain about almost everything.


